<h3>[12-and-under] Lakeville South Fall traveling league!</h3>
<p>
	Love volleyball and are looking for more competition?
	Consider joining one of our fall 12-and-under teams. 
	Lakeville South will sponsor several teams in the South Suburban Youth Volleyball league. 
	Plan on joining us for a fun and competitive volleyball season this fall! 
	More details and how to <%= link_to "pre-register online", form_href, :target => '_blank' %> are below. 
</p>
